webpackJsonp([2],{157:function(e,a){e.exports="<p>As I’ve previously said before, legendary-pancake is an <strong><em>advanced</em></strong> tool, so it doesn’t try to abstract away from the intricacies of webpack.</p> <h1>Setting up the project</h1> <p>Create an empty directory for your website:</p> <pre><code class=language-sh>mkdir my-site\n<span class=hljs-built_in>cd</span> my-site\n</code></pre> <p>Initialize a package:</p> <pre><code class=language-sh>yarn init -y\n</code></pre> <p>Install legendary-pancake:</p> <pre><code class=language-sh>yarn add --dev legendary-pancake\n</code></pre> <p>More info later lol</p> "}});